{"tid":293231,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳曾任夜場公關 「間尺鼻」Angelica：好多人唔鍾意我！","createTime":"2017-06-22T04:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T17:27:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5250143df0457a597aa0984c25c7993ae9263aeb","tid":293231,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:08:08.000Z","msg":"《香港小姐競選2017》喺前日進行首輪面試，喺131個面試佳麗入面，有唔少都符合花生友嘅口味，其中一位自稱叫Angelica嘅女仔，芳齡25歲，嗰個又直又長嘅鼻，兩邊嘅蘋果肌又異常豐滿，結果「間尺鼻」Angelica成為整日焦點，網上瘋傳關於佢嘅報道，連帶突然多咗好多佢嘅舊照，好多朋友爆料講佢嘅背景！(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sP5Dao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sP5Dao&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=720fcf1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sP5Dao</a>)<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，原來呢位Angelica喺15年曾以「何沛沂」為名，簽約信星亞太娛樂，嗰陣佢同嚟自大陸嘅MK Pop組合拾音社屬同門，不過只係曇花一現，估唔到事隔兩年走去參選港姐！<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170622/56858400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170622%2F56858400&d=17n4cqxg%2B2J6khD3gA7q%2BC7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=bb9b3ff5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170622%2F56858400&h=914730e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170622/56858400</a></div><br />\n<br />\n噚日《蘋果》致電Angelica，講到首輪面試情況，佢話：「我完全唔知乜嘢事，覺得好似俾人攞嚟炒作，其實啲對話乜嘢都冇回應過！」又稱：「都有影響心情，唔知點解影出嚟啲相咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，皮膚又好差，我啲朋友話真人唔會咁樣，參選者都有百幾個，但係好似特別針對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！」唔知有冇諗過唔再玩？佢話：「我都想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但係我身邊啲朋友話：『你都參選咗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！』。」<br />\n<br />\n那面試期間可曾向無綫交代曾任Model？Angelica表示話：「冇呀，面試嗰陣從來都冇提過以前做model，其實好多嘢我都唔想再公開。我覺得啲人好似想攞我嚟炒作。我只係平平淡淡，而且TVB都叫我哋唔好講咁多嘢，只係簡單講自己個名。」<br />\n<br />\n據知第二輪面試將會喺下個星期進行，但係Angelica被問幾時再通知第二輪？佢話：「我印象中應該係會打電話通知。有冇信心？我都唔知，我都俾人炒到咁樣，其實如果真實認識我啲人，都知我唔係嗰啲騎呢，但係如果覺得我要行嗰啲路線，都冇辦法。」再問佢如果入唔到圍會唔會再喺娛樂圈發展？佢話：「我都唔知，唔回應喇，因為大台都唔俾我講咁多嘢。」"},{"pid":"3975066f4d3301c0b38433045a063e657701826e","tid":293231,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498047270_93d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498047270_93d1.jpg&h=625edd69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"97a1c3d9112c6cab6b7aa25e864a16e2af1be6ef","tid":293231,"uid":51890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:17:05.000Z","msg":"佢嗰啲真係朋友嚟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de53ddce478c24c8e1a8685bfe87ef50441948a3","tid":293231,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"屌你真係好撚樣衰"},{"pid":"a306cf1ed5f8150351c6a598f1734ce33c7114cb","tid":293231,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你真係好撚樣衰</blockquote><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498047276_386f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498047276_386f.jpg&h=dbb332e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">佢投訴話：「唔知點解影出嚟啲相咁樣衰，皮膚又好差，我啲朋友話真人唔會咁樣！」</span></div>"},{"pid":"458184fef611993c6ce9f7810afddff1e40d0b62","tid":293231,"uid":37501,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"個鼻去左大陸整？<br />\n整容失敗咁都夠膽去參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184afcc569a02f2ba4a7fb38b17de47ccb5fae0","tid":293231,"uid":232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"reply